## Database Architecture Requirements (Supabase)

The AI Agent must ensure the following tables are created (with RLS enabled) in the Supabase project:

1. `user_profiles`: `id` (references `auth.users`), `partner_1_name`, `partner_2_name`, `wedding_date`, `total_guest_count`, `state`, `lga`.
2. `user_events`: `id`, `user_id`, `event_name`, `date`, `time`, `venue_id`, `status`.
3. `user_budgets`: `id`, `user_id`, `category`, `estimated_cost`, `actual_cost`, `paid_amount`, `vendor_name`.
4. `venues_catalog` (Admin controlled, read-only for users): `id`, `name`, `state`, `lga`, `base_price`, `max_capacity`, `description`.

